## 2. Business Rules

| Rule | MГҙ tбәЈ | Enforcement |
|------|--------|-------------|
| **R1** | Hб»§y enrollment = soft delete, khГҙng hard delete | вң… BбәҜt buб»ҷc |
| **R2** | ДҗГЈ cГі payment вҶ’ cбәЈnh bГЎo nhЖ°ng vбә«n cho hб»§y (giб»Ҝ payment) | вҡ пёҸ Warning dialog |
